---
title: Katsu Chicken Curry with broccoli, coriander and chilli
description: Our take on the familiar favourite Japanese dish: Katsu Curry. Perfectly crispy crumbed chicken breast sitting on a bed of fluffy rice is smothered with a delicious katsu curry sauce in this fabulous fakeaway. Steam-fried broccoli and fresh coriander add plenty of colour and crunch.
